ro]]\n|'''{{vb-big|BRA}}'''\n|'''3\u20130'''\n|{{vb-big|ITA}}\n|{{vb-big|USA}}\n|'''3\u20132'''\n|{{vb-big|RUS}}\n|12\n|- \n|2020<br />[[Volleyball at the 2020 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|Details]]\n|{{flagicon|JPN}}<br>[[Tokyo]]\n|\n|'''\u2013'''\n|\n|\n|'''\u2013'''\n|\n|12\n|- bgcolor=#E8E8F0\n|2024<br />[[Volleyball at the 2024 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|Details]]\n|{{flagicon|FRA}}<br>[[Paris]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n===Participating nations===\n;Legend\n*{{bg|gold|1st}} \u2013 Gold medalists\n*{{bg|silver|2nd}} \u2013 Silver medalists\n*{{bg|#cc9966|3rd}} \u2013 Bronze medalists\n*{{bg|#9acdff|4th}} \u2013 4th place\n*{{border|width=1px|color=gray|&nbsp;\u2022&nbsp;}} \u2013 Did not enter / Did not qualify\n*{{border|width=3px|color=red|&nbsp;&nbsp;}} \u2013 Hosts\n*= \u2013 More than one team tied for that rank\n*Q \u2013 Qualified for forthcoming tournament\n\n{| class=\"wikitable shortable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:90%\"\n|- bgcolor=\n|'''Team'''\n||{{flagicon|JPN|1870}}<br>'''[[Volleyball at the 1964 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|1964]]'''<br>(10)\n||{{flagicon|MEX|1934}}<br>'''[[Volleyball at the 1968 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|1968]]'''<br>(10)\n||{{flagicon|FRG}}<br>'''[[Volleyball at the 1972 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|1972]]'''<br>(12)\n||{{flagicon|CAN}}<br>'''[[Volleyball at the 1976 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|1976]]'''<br>(10)\n||{{flagicon|URS|1955}}<br>'''[[Volleyball at the 1980 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|1980]]'''<br>(10)\n||{{flagicon|USA}}<br>'''[[Volleyball at the 1984 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|1984]]'''<br>(10)\n||{{flagicon|KOR|1984}}<br>'''[[Volleyball at the 1988 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|1988]]'''<br>(12)\n||{{flagicon|ESP}}<br>'''[[Volleyball at the 1992 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|1992]]'''<br>(12)\n||{{flagicon|USA}}<br>'''[[Volleyball at the 1996 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|